		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Swapping a 3d model is neither simple nor easy, especially on a console game.
<br />It'd involve allot of remapping since I'm sure the texture would fit if you just swapped 'em.
<br />
<br />
<br />PC games aren't so hard, well not the mod friendly games anyway.
<br />(gta3 anyone?)

		

